1
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:55,580
=Episode 3=

3
00:00:55,620 --> 00:00:58,180
(Three days later)

4
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:04,319
Your Highness.

5
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:05,760
Ling Xiao is out of danger.

6
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:07,359
But...

7
00:01:07,879 --> 00:01:08,560
Don't hide it.

8
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:10,280
But I have a feeling

9
00:01:10,719 --> 00:01:12,280
that Ling Xiao
seems to be hiding something.

10
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:14,079
I checked his wounds.

11
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:15,439
They appear fatal on the surface,

12
00:01:15,959 --> 00:01:17,040
yet precisely

13
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:18,439
avoided every vital spot.

14
00:01:21,840 --> 00:01:23,760
This man has come for me many times.

15
00:01:23,959 --> 00:01:24,959
It's way too deliberate.

16
00:01:25,879 --> 00:01:27,159
He survived the assassination,

17
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,439
yet still chose to enter the palace.

18
00:01:30,159 --> 00:01:31,799
I suspect his true purpose

19
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:33,280
is anything but simple.

20
00:01:34,599 --> 00:01:35,640
I'll keep a close watch.

21
00:01:36,319 --> 00:01:37,959
If I catch him in any disloyal act,

22
00:01:38,319 --> 00:01:39,120
I'll kill him on the spot.

23
00:01:56,239 --> 00:01:56,719
Don't move.

24
00:01:56,879 --> 00:01:57,480
Let me do it.

25
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:58,400
Sorry.

26
00:01:59,079 --> 00:01:59,640
Sorry.

27
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,520
(Medical Case Record)

28
00:02:16,639 --> 00:02:18,639
You're lucky to be alive.

29
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:20,960
If the stab had missed by a fraction,

30
00:02:21,159 --> 00:02:22,439
you would have died.

31
00:02:22,879 --> 00:02:24,800
I heard Her Highness was unwell
some time ago.

32
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:27,759
I wonder if she has recovered now?

33
00:02:28,919 --> 00:02:30,719
I have been deeply worried.

34
00:02:31,159 --> 00:02:33,199
Her Highness is indeed blessed.
She recovered long ago.

35
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:41,840
I didn't expect you to
care so much about me.

36
00:02:43,439 --> 00:02:46,680
Doesn't Your Highness care
just as much about me?

37
00:02:48,719 --> 00:02:50,000
It was hard to tell before,

38
00:02:51,199 --> 00:02:52,120
but now,

39
00:02:52,919 --> 00:02:56,120
I find myself more curious
than worried about you.

40
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:59,800
I have passed the trial
of life and death,

41
00:03:00,479 --> 00:03:02,360
but am I still not qualified to
enter the Ruyi Palace?

42
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:09,039
You're that eager to
step into my chamber,

43
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,879
to be noticed by me,

44
00:03:11,199 --> 00:03:12,639
and to earn my grace?

45
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:17,719
Or are you trying to use
the imperial physician

46
00:03:18,039 --> 00:03:19,240
to spy on medical records

47
00:03:19,599 --> 00:03:21,520
and obtain intelligence or secrets?

48
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,439
Your Highness.

49
00:03:25,719 --> 00:03:27,240
Do you remember my slave mark?

50
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:28,759
Please look at it.

51
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,400
You can tell that I've borne it
since childhood.

52
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,400
How could I have spent years scheming

53
00:03:32,759 --> 00:03:34,039
to get close to you?

54
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:37,120
You simply don't wish to
truly understand

55
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:39,000
a lowly person like me.

56
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:41,199
By saying that,

57
00:03:41,919 --> 00:03:43,400
so now it's my fault?

58
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:45,960
You are the most honored person
in Xiling.

59
00:03:46,919 --> 00:03:48,400
After unifying Dongqing,

60
00:03:49,199 --> 00:03:51,960
you will be the sovereign
of the land of Furong.

61
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:54,199
All my scheming and efforts

62
00:03:55,199 --> 00:03:56,840
are only to stay by your side

63
00:03:57,639 --> 00:04:00,879
for a stable life with food and wear,

64
00:04:01,439 --> 00:04:02,159
and I seek

65
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:03,840
something I long for

66
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,840
yet cannot have, the respect.

67
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:22,519
If you take this cup of tea,

68
00:04:24,399 --> 00:04:25,720
it might as well be a marriage to me.

69
00:04:38,839 --> 00:04:39,879
Well then,

70
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,639
you may stay.

71
00:04:46,079 --> 00:04:47,639
I wish to hold your hand

72
00:04:49,519 --> 00:04:50,639
and grow old with you.

73
00:04:54,839 --> 00:04:55,360
Your Highness!

74
00:04:56,199 --> 00:04:56,720
Your Highness!

75
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:57,879
Your Highness!

76
00:04:58,199 --> 00:04:58,680
Your Highness!

77
00:04:58,680 --> 00:04:59,160
Your Highness!

78
00:04:59,160 --> 00:04:59,759
Your Highness!

79
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:00,560
Your Highness!

80
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:05,839
Your Majesty,
the Princess has suddenly fallen ill.

81
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,959
She has caught a chill again.

82
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:09,160
It doesn't look good.

83
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:13,680
The Princess's illness isn't ordinary.

84
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,519
She is now in a coma
and struggling to breathe.

85
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,879
If we don't open her chest with a blade,

86
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,839
she may not wake up.

87
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:24,920
Your Majesty,

88
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:27,199
the Princess is at death's door.

89
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:29,560
Please save her!

90
00:05:34,199 --> 00:05:36,360
You expect me to trust a slave?

91
00:05:37,279 --> 00:05:38,240
I am the only one

92
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:39,839
willing to give my life
for the Princess.

93
00:05:42,319 --> 00:05:43,839
If the Princess does not wake,

94
00:05:45,279 --> 00:05:46,439
for any reason,

95
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,759
I will never leave this mansion alive.

96
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,839
Though risky,

97
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:53,319
this is recorded in ancient texts.

98
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,639
We have no choice but to try.

99
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:57,199
If you fail...

100
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:58,360
I...

101
00:05:58,879 --> 00:05:59,959
I stake my life on it.

102
00:06:01,079 --> 00:06:02,319
I will bring the Princess back.

103
00:06:02,959 --> 00:06:04,279
Then what are you waiting for?

104
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:07,279
The remedy still lacks
its final ingredient,

105
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:09,600
the blood from the same person.

106
00:06:10,439 --> 00:06:12,560
For seven whole days,
without a single break.

107
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:14,160
An ordinary person

108
00:06:14,759 --> 00:06:16,680
would hardly endure such torment.

109
00:06:17,319 --> 00:06:20,160
There is a risk of death.

110
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:21,920
Xia Ke'er.

111
00:06:22,279 --> 00:06:23,160
Go to your army

112
00:06:23,519 --> 00:06:25,759
and find a general willing to give blood
for the Princess.

113
00:06:26,759 --> 00:06:27,279
Yes.

114
00:06:28,079 --> 00:06:28,600
Your Majesty,

115
00:06:30,079 --> 00:06:31,240
there's no need to search far.

116
00:06:31,759 --> 00:06:33,160
I am willing to give my blood

117
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:35,639
and save the Princess.

118
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,519
Then you

119
00:06:39,759 --> 00:06:41,319
must save my daughter.

120
00:06:44,620 --> 00:06:48,820
(Seven days later)

121
00:07:16,199 --> 00:07:17,639
Your Highness, you're awake!

122
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:20,279
The Princess is awake.

123
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,000
What happened?

124
00:07:25,199 --> 00:07:26,680
You were struck by a sudden illness,

125
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,000
gravely.

126
00:07:29,199 --> 00:07:31,000
Mr. Ling gave his blood as medicine

127
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,639
for seven days

128
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,759
and cured you of your severe illness.

129
00:07:35,959 --> 00:07:36,680
I never imagined

130
00:07:37,199 --> 00:07:38,879
Mr. Ling would risk his life
to save you.

131
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:43,000
You've recovered.

132
00:07:43,879 --> 00:07:46,240
That's... that's good.

133
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:48,160
Ling Xiao!

134
00:07:48,439 --> 00:07:49,160
Ling Xiao!

135
00:07:49,319 --> 00:07:50,000
Ling Xiao!

136
00:07:51,639 --> 00:07:52,439
Ling Xiao!

137
00:07:57,839 --> 00:07:58,480
Your Highness.

138
00:08:00,839 --> 00:08:01,879
Today is the Winter Solstice.

139
00:08:02,199 --> 00:08:04,000
I heard the markets are bustling
with festivity.

140
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,079
Care to go out for a look?

141
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:08,000
I went to see Ling Xiao
before I came here.

142
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,480
He still won't leave his room.

143
00:08:10,959 --> 00:08:12,199
Didn't the imperial physician say

144
00:08:12,439 --> 00:08:14,199
that Mr. Ling is out of danger?

145
00:08:14,439 --> 00:08:15,519
There's no need for you to worry.

146
00:08:17,399 --> 00:08:18,800
Your Highness, your mood

147
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,240
is like the stars in the sky,

148
00:08:21,399 --> 00:08:22,360
changeable and unpredictable.

149
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:25,959
Didn't you say
Mr. Ling was highly suspicious,

150
00:08:26,279 --> 00:08:27,519
and if I caught any sign of trouble,

151
00:08:27,959 --> 00:08:28,839
I should kill him on the spot?

152
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:32,440
But he saved me again and again.

153
00:08:33,519 --> 00:08:36,679
Perhaps I should trust him once.

154
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:41,639
Go to the market

155
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:43,519
and snap up every curious treasure

156
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:44,360
on the street and bring them to me.

157
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:48,320
Your Highness, you're so generous!

158
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:49,639
It's a reward for all my hard work

159
00:08:49,759 --> 00:08:51,559
and service by your side this year.

160
00:08:52,679 --> 00:08:53,919
Yours is separate.

161
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:56,879
All of this is for Ling Xiao.

162
00:09:00,039 --> 00:09:00,600
Now, go.

163
00:09:01,559 --> 00:09:02,039
Go!

164
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:20,279
Ling Xiao.

165
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:21,879
- Your Highness.
- Be seated.

166
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:26,639
You have not fully recovered.
You should not walk out.

167
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,080
I'm sorry to have caused you concern,
Your Highness.

168
00:09:28,279 --> 00:09:29,559
Thankfully, you are safe.

169
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:32,559
Otherwise,
I would have been taken for a spy

170
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:34,320
and killed in the Ruyi Palace.

171
00:09:36,279 --> 00:09:37,080
Today is the Winter Solstice.

172
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:39,559
I made a small gift for you.

173
00:09:40,399 --> 00:09:42,639
One roly-poly toy feels alone.

174
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,120
Why not take this festive day

175
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,200
to find it a companion?

176
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,240
May they never be separated.

177
00:09:50,399 --> 00:09:51,639
You made this yourself?

178
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,639
I was born in the countryside.

179
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,279
This is the skill I can rely on.

180
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:59,840
My father was skilled in wood carving.

181
00:10:00,519 --> 00:10:03,080
I cried a lot when I was little,

182
00:10:04,279 --> 00:10:06,000
so my father would make wooden toys

183
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:06,639
to soothe me.

184
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,240
Unfortunately,

185
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:10,960
on every festive occasion,

186
00:10:12,639 --> 00:10:14,159
I can no longer be with my loved ones.

187
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:20,080
I too have long forgotten Father's face.

188
00:10:23,279 --> 00:10:25,480
Yet I can still recall his laughter.

189
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:27,960
Whenever I cried,

190
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:30,360
he would take out this roly-poly toy

191
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:32,360
and comfort me with a smile.

192
00:10:32,879 --> 00:10:33,600
In the end,

193
00:10:34,159 --> 00:10:35,399
all that remains

194
00:10:35,799 --> 00:10:37,360
is this smiling roly-poly toy

195
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,480
that reminds me of Father.

196
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:47,000
Though you sit in a high place

197
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,320
and I am but a lowly servant,

198
00:10:50,559 --> 00:10:52,399
we can't escape
the pain of losing loved ones

199
00:10:52,759 --> 00:10:54,039
and the longing for our fathers.

200
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:56,399
It's the same for both of us.

201
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:59,159
It's been a long time
since I've received

202
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:00,559
a gift I've loved this much.

203
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:02,320
What would you like in return?

204
00:11:02,919 --> 00:11:03,759
Your Highness, how about

205
00:11:04,519 --> 00:11:06,679
you give this pair of roly-poly toys
a name?

206
00:11:09,879 --> 00:11:11,080
Then we call them

207
00:11:11,639 --> 00:11:12,720
"United Forever in Harmony"

208
00:11:13,399 --> 00:11:14,240
and "Standing Firm, Never Falling".

209
00:11:34,039 --> 00:11:34,799
Your Majesty.

210
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:37,000
This journey into Xiling
is fraught with peril.

211
00:11:37,639 --> 00:11:39,120
Just as we suspected,

212
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:41,120
Mu Ruyi is cautious and suspicious.

213
00:11:41,559 --> 00:11:42,840
Maybe we should return to Dongqing first

214
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:43,840
and discuss it at length.

215
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:46,679
Mo Shuo.

216
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:49,480
Now that I have met Mu Ruyi,

217
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:52,480
I will not give up so easily.

218
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:53,679
Your Majesty.

219
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:57,879
Ling Xiao,

220
00:11:58,519 --> 00:11:59,320
please consider this carefully.

221
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:06,679
Mu Ruyi,

222
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:08,559
from this day,

223
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:12,320
you will never escape my grasp.
